<span id="freeTextContainer14925747532771060505"><b>What tended to happen, to Colin and Mary at least, was that subjects were not explored so much as defensively reiterated, or forced into elaborate irrelevancies, and suffused with irritability.</b><br/><br/>This slim weapon is a foggy retreat into the nuptual neuroses during the holiday abroad. All baggage isn&apos;t declared at Customs. The soul is a mule through Passport Control. Regret and doubt are the rogue&apos;s liquidity, the same for the spouse. Lifting Blanche&apos;s best line will ultimately avail with kinky prop</span>
  <span id="freeText14925747532771060505" style="display:none"><b>What tended to happen, to Colin and Mary at least, was that subjects were not explored so much as defensively reiterated, or forced into elaborate irrelevancies, and suffused with irritability.</b><br /><br />This slim weapon is a foggy retreat into the nuptual neuroses during the holiday abroad. All baggage isn't declared at Customs. The soul is a mule through Passport Control. Regret and doubt are the rogue's liquidity, the same for the spouse. Lifting Blanche's best line will ultimately avail with kinky proposals and a nightlight stilleto. Beware.</span>
